{"tid":647810,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"大陸高中教生命的可貴　要學生孵化小雞養大再宰吃","createTime":"2018-04-30T07:04:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-30T13:20:59.000Z","uid":132227,"like":7,"dislike":56,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"9f91fa2a9e5c46194c88520567c415a14c72067d","tid":647810,"uid":132227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T07:04:17.000Z","msg":"中國的出雲南第一高中，為了讓學生明白生命的可貴，開辦了一門名為「孵蛋養雞再吃掉」的課程，已有60年歷史。學生期間要孵化小雞，悉心養大牠們，最後要親手烹煮並吃掉，一眾學生由看着新生命誕生的笑臉變成淚流滿面。網民反應兩極，有人質疑該校教育的只是「一切皆可拋的殘忍」。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/30/150332_5119b107b9783ce9ce849ac3ce533846.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F30%2F150332_5119b107b9783ce9ce849ac3ce533846.jpg&h=9f090d6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新一年度、為期半年的課程於去年10月開始，紀錄片中可見，學生在首日先準備好孵化雞蛋，確認所需的溫度及濕度，並將蛋放入孵蛋器。約60隻的小雞在三周後開始一隻接一隻孵化，令學生無不感到開心。孵化後約一個月，學生開始學習飼養小雞，每日輪流更換雞舍的水，並拍攝小雞的成長紀錄，看着牠們逐漸羽翼長成。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/30/150351_244b906e7066d81d441e87694adea0ba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F30%2F150351_244b906e7066d81d441e87694adea0ba.jpg&h=a2497894&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n至上月，學生最後一次為牠們測體重，便要在老師的指導下，學習屠宰並烹調雞隻。有女生哭唸「對不起」甚至擁抱痛哭。導師高橋表示，家畜作為食物被人吸收作養分，希望學生在養育至吃掉雞隻的過程中，明白生命的可貴。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/30/150408_f51eb70f1ae0402125272b0d946214ac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F30%2F150408_f51eb70f1ae0402125272b0d946214ac.jpg&h=e65ad030&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有網民支持有關課程，直言「生命教育本來就殘忍」；亦有人強調「好好吃掉不浪費，就是對食物最大的感謝」。但亦有網民批評課程「變態」，有人更質問：「先讓學生付出半年的關愛，再把半年的心血吃掉，真的在教導生命的可貴嗎？抑或一切皆可拋的殘忍？」<br />\n<br />\n支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"696c9d1aa4f9a626130a9888e8d2384c1ea4948e","tid":647810,"uid":26030,"like":64,"dislike":1,"score":63,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T07:06:10.000Z","msg":"改日本新聞？"},{"pid":"5bf3687c1479e3d01b334e8b254facc08a408434","tid":647810,"uid":128055,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T07:06:41.000Z","msg":"唔知有無記錯, 好似銀之匙的劇情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f14eacaee2a99dd50b1a20bd06bd04904c71f909","tid":647810,"uid":131686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T07:06:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccf96dc76593a7b182d2a223cc71c034c4181ba0","tid":647810,"uid":62815,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T07:09:51.000Z","msg":"等睇撞車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"392fc1df37330382d3851f2b2e6eccb365401e77","tid":647810,"uid":184511,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T07:13:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"00184ee96d6475559e89aea289e8d5eb517b5c40","tid":647810,"uid":89514,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T07:18:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"28062009d0d80d9232eb179236a68f03cde550bc","tid":647810,"uid":61094,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T07:22:58.000Z","msg":"大陸點會搞咁麻煩嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8aced29885b3dc932e5e5336a982c3263286b80","tid":647810,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T07:24:53.000Z","msg":"大陸高中。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1228af554e1361dffdbb1b41107fb91f73f0bfd","tid":647810,"uid":43173,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T07:26:32.000Z","msg":"做法ok，但覺得有乜60年歷史好撚假<br />\n結論，一係鳩噏，一係改新聞<br />\n請俾link"},{"pid":"e6fc11addcaad4bc8ca3203e174c382dfd02b3e1","tid":647810,"uid":69291,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T07:27:33.000Z","msg":"▲▼要求學生「吃掉養了半年的小雞」。(圖／翻攝自梨視頻秒拍)<br />\n▲學生們認真做紀錄，孵養小雞。(圖／翻攝自梨視頻秒拍)<br />\n<br />\n記者楊蕙綾／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n為了讓學生了解生命的可貴，日本島根縣出雲農林高中去年10月開設一門「孵化小雞，養大後再吃掉」的課程，當課程逐漸進入尾聲，學生們也淚流不止。新聞引發網友熱論，話題也登上微博熱搜排行榜！<br />\n<br />\n「梨視頻」影片可見，課程開始首日，學生們先做好孵化雞蛋的準備，確認孵化所需的溫度及濕度，再將雞蛋放入孵蛋器內，約莫三周後，一隻隻黃澄澄的小雞順利孵化，學生們也感到十分開心。<br />\n<br />\n一個月後，雞隻全數孵化，確認培育箱的溫度及濕度後，學生們正式養育雞隻，每天輪流更換雞舍內飲水，也會替小雞拍攝成長紀錄，今年三月中旬，小雞們完美變身成雞，學生們最後一次替牠們測量體重，這也代表課程即將進入尾聲。<br />\n<br />\n影片中可見，在老師的指導下，學生們兩兩一組進行宰殺課程，當場逼哭在場所有學生，女學生流著淚、啜泣對雞隻說「對不起」，還有學生擁抱痛哭，場面令人不捨。<br />\n<br />\n▲▼要求學生「吃掉養了半年的小雞」。(圖／翻攝自梨視頻秒拍)<br />\n<br />\n▲要求學生「吃掉養了半年的小雞」，學生泣不成聲。(圖／翻攝自梨視頻秒拍)<br />\n<br />\n解體課程結束後，老師教導學生烹飪方法，只要將煮熟後的雞肉吃下肚，這堂為期半年的課程便正式畫下句點。班導師高橋表示，家畜作為食物被人吸收成養分，在養育生命最後把牠們吃掉的過程中，可以讓學生了解生命的重要。<br />\n<br />\n影片曝光後引發網友正反面討論，有網友直呼「生命教育本身就是殘忍的」、「對食物最大的感謝就是好好吃掉不要浪費」、「怎麼感覺是雞業養殖課」、「然而我們農村人把雞鴨養大，就是為了下蛋然後吃掉啊 但是如果是自己養的狗就絕對做不到了」、「評論很多都沒有看過《銀之匙》」。<br />\n<br />\n也有網友質疑「先讓其付出半年的關愛，然後又把半年的心血吃掉，教育的真是生命的可貴？還是一切皆可拋的殘忍？」、「我覺得這門課上的並不是生命可貴，而是面對自己有感情的事物如何冷漠對待，人之所以稱自己是靈長動物，不就是因為有情感和智商，這門課確實有點變態了」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20180429/1159723.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20180429%2F1159723.htm&d=c0IW%2Fu7PGTltYwpW2bMHqhv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=98992299\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20180429/1159723.htm</a>"},{"pid":"de5946c8862f31224ca33756a5c815d86d62b138","tid":647810,"uid":24393,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T07:28:29.000Z","msg":"樓主支那人想誤導連登仔失敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed6436b22945b0de60d6c9507557235b29cfffb8","tid":647810,"uid":15813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T07:28:38.000Z","msg":"出雲南<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n改新聞"},{"pid":"f59a24a988dcb48168556b6d3161756bf5bfcb68","tid":647810,"uid":83102,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"de5946c8862f31224ca33756a5c815d86d62b138","tid":647810,"uid":24393,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T07:28:29.000Z","msg":"樓主支那人想誤導連登仔失敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T07:32:20.000Z","msg":"佢一定笑住咁出post<br />\n想連登仔回應 屌鳩蝗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b851a9c5b999dafcd46c33cee731f8382b4b5fd7","tid":647810,"uid":52215,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T07:33:11.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<br />\n連登仔反支反上腦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db10117299c937d38e057291e3b0a0d96a9d99e4","tid":647810,"uid":30085,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T07:34:24.000Z","msg":"改新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"855d46932c65db2075aa2dead6adcff70c838223","tid":647810,"uid":61864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T08:00:19.000Z","msg":"自己食左隻雞可以學到咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b693c70c20fbdabf946ee3277d3a66ebdd7117bf","tid":647810,"uid":35648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T08:01:41.000Z","msg":"出雲南<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"078b86dfa836c348e18a6a3a7e1db33c56909255","tid":647810,"uid":122101,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T08:02:42.000Z","msg":"銀之匙要自己學養豬，然後劏左佢學整煙肉"},{"pid":"81600849c85278b2f383a3c6f4a544b9031275c5","tid":647810,"uid":179967,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T08:04:11.000Z","msg":"將標題頭兩隻字大陸改做美國<br />\n正負評就會調翻轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfdc7c6e7c2928118eb9ac38113375bfd46cb3f2","tid":647810,"uid":155853,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T08:04:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中國的出雲南第一高中，為了讓學生明白生命的可貴，開辦了一門名為「孵蛋養雞再吃掉」的課程，已有60年歷史。學生期間要孵化小雞，悉心養大牠們，最後要親手烹煮並吃掉，一眾學生由看着新生命誕生的笑臉變成淚流滿面。網民反應兩極，有人質疑該校教育的只是「一切皆可拋的殘忍」。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/30/150332_5119b107b9783ce9ce849ac3ce533846.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F30%2F150332_5119b107b9783ce9ce849ac3ce533846.jpg&h=9f090d6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新一年度、為期半年的課程於去年10月開始，紀錄片中可見，學生在首日先準備好孵化雞蛋，確認所需的溫度及濕度，並將蛋放入孵蛋器。約60隻的小雞在三周後開始一隻接一隻孵化，令學生無不感到開心。孵化後約一個月，學生開始學習飼養小雞，每日輪流更換雞舍的水，並拍攝小雞的成長紀錄，看着牠們逐漸羽翼長成。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/30/150351_244b906e7066d81d441e87694adea0ba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F30%2F150351_244b906e7066d81d441e87694adea0ba.jpg&h=a2497894&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n至上月，學生最後一次為牠們測體重，便要在老師的指導下，學習屠宰並烹調雞隻。有女生哭唸「對不起」甚至擁抱痛哭。導師<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">高橋</span></span>表示，家畜作為食物被人吸收作養分，希望學生在養育至吃掉雞隻的過程中，明白生命的可貴。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/30/150408_f51eb70f1ae0402125272b0d946214ac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F30%2F150408_f51eb70f1ae0402125272b0d946214ac.jpg&h=e65ad030&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有網民支持有關課程，直言「生命教育本來就殘忍」；亦有人強調「好好吃掉不浪費，就是對食物最大的感謝」。但亦有網民批評課程「變態」，有人更質問：「先讓學生付出半年的關愛，再把半年的心血吃掉，真的在教導生命的可貴嗎？抑或一切皆可拋的殘忍？」<br />\n<br />\n支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"3a8d350694a6e1db744abd4d29d749106efbcbb7","tid":647810,"uid":139815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T08:15:50.000Z","msg":"支那人真係無血性<br />\n咁無恥既做法都做得出<br />\n做得出呢啲事既國家,鬼唔望佢地俾人滅國"},{"pid":"5439b11f7d5bfbb3cc58812ff39761e8f8fba83b","tid":647810,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T08:17:53.000Z","msg":"Ettoday<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47be13e0f6fd3ca0050ed5470826560a088eb534","tid":647810,"uid":56999,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T08:19:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n支那人<br />\n<br />\n到了學期末<br />\n準備把雞殺到吃<br />\n<br />\n發現一隻雞都沒有<br />\n<br />\n原來有的人雞還未長大就拿去賣了<br />\n<br />\n有的人把買飼料的錢私吞了<br />\n把雞餓死了<br />\n<br />\n大家都想，少了一隻雞沒關係<br />\n殺其他人的雞就夠吃了"},{"pid":"b50d68ce1ff8b1604d9a8c30c562f4ee2887b5b4","tid":647810,"uid":184511,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T08:21:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}